OL,3,CTributes to former Labour MP Doug
OL,4,CHoyle who has died aged 98
OL,6,FSir Lindsay said his whole family are
OL,7,Fdevastated.
OL,9,F"There are few people who get to my
OL,10,Fage with their father still around `
OL,11,Fbut I have been one of the lucky
OL,12,Fones," he added.
OL,14,F"His death last night has left me
OL,15,Fbereft ` I have lost my dad, my
OL,16,Finspiration and the country has lost a
OL,17,Ftruly dedicated parliamentarian."
